### token exchange (EXCHANGE 프리셋 client).. Basic 은 EXCHANGE 등록 응답의 client_id:client_secret 를 base64 인코딩해 교체
### {subject token} 은 authorization_code_grant 로 받은 사용자 access token
### resource 는 등록 시 지정한 allowedResources 안의 값이어야 한다.. 발급 토큰은 sub 유지 + aud 에 대상 자원 반영
POST http://localhost:9000/oauth2/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Basic {base64(client_id:client_secret)}

grant_type=urn:ietf:params:oauth:grant-type:token-exchange&
subject_token={subject token}&
subject_token_type=urn:ietf:params:oauth:token-type:access_token&
scope=custom-scope&
resource=https://comment.example.com

### 허용 목록을 벗어난 resource 요청 -> 400 invalid_target (발급 측 통제.. RFC 8707)
POST http://localhost:9000/oauth2/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Basic {base64(client_id:client_secret)}

grant_type=urn:ietf:params:oauth:grant-type:token-exchange&
subject_token={subject token}&
subject_token_type=urn:ietf:params:oauth:token-type:access_token&
resource=https://article.example.com
